@startuml
top to bottom direction
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam nodesep 30
skinparam ranksep 40
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #F8FAFC
  BorderColor #475569
}
skinparam database {
  BackgroundColor #FEF3C7
  BorderColor #B45309
}
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #FFF7ED
  BorderColor #C2410C
}

title EduSecure Current-State Data Flow Diagram - Level 1

rectangle "Client Boundary" {
  rectangle "Browser Users\n(Auth + MFA)\n<<External Entity>>" as UsersAuth #E0F2FE
  rectangle "Authenticator App\n(user-operated TOTP)\n<<External Entity>>" as Authenticator #E0F2FE
  database "D0 Browser sessionStorage\nPending MFA challenge copied from login response\n(cleared after MFA / no JWT)" as D0
  rectangle "Browser Users\n(Submissions / Grades / Spaces)\n<<External Entity>>" as UsersAcademic #E0F2FE

  UsersAuth -[hidden]right-> Authenticator
  Authenticator -[hidden]right-> D0
  D0 -[hidden]right-> UsersAcademic
}

rectangle "EduSecure Application Boundary" {
  rectangle "Identity & Access" {
    rectangle "P1 Auth & Session\nAuthController + AuthService" as P1 #DBEAFE
    rectangle "P2 MFA Challenge\nMfaService" as P2 #DBEAFE
    P1 -[hidden]right-> P2
  }

  rectangle "Academic Operations" {
    rectangle "P7 Assignment Access\n& Creation\nAssignmentService" as P7 #DBEAFE
    rectangle "P3 Submission Protection\n& Retrieval\nSubmissionService" as P3 #DBEAFE
    rectangle "P4 Grade Integrity\nHandling\nGradeService" as P4 #DBEAFE
    rectangle "P6 Space Ownership\n& Membership\nSpaceService" as P6 #DBEAFE
    P7 -[hidden]right-> P3
    P3 -[hidden]right-> P4
    P4 -[hidden]right-> P6
  }

  rectangle "Audit & Assurance" {
    rectangle "P5 Audit Integrity\nRecording\nAuditService" as P5 #DBEAFE
  }

  P1 -[hidden]down-> P7
  P2 -[hidden]down-> P4
  P4 -[hidden]down-> P5
}

rectangle "Persistence Boundary" {
  database "D2 Submission Ciphertext Store\nDefault file-system ciphertext store\nby storedFileReference" as D2
  database "D1 PostgreSQL\nUsers, roles, assignments, spaces, memberships,\nMFA metadata, submission metadata, grades, audit logs" as D1
  D2 -[hidden]right-> D1
}

UsersAuth -[hidden]down-> P1
Authenticator -[hidden]down-> P2
D0 -[hidden]down-> P2
UsersAcademic -[hidden]down-> P7
P3 -[hidden]down-> D2
P5 -[hidden]down-> D1

UsersAuth <--> P1 : Auth exchange\n(register / login / logout / session)
UsersAuth <--> P2 : MFA setup material /\nverify / disable
UsersAuth <--> Authenticator : manual TOTP setup\n+ code reading for browser entry
P1 <--> P2 : MFA challenge start / result
P1 <--> D1 : User, role, and\npassword-hash data
P1 --> UsersAuth : MFA_REQUIRED response\nwith challenge data
UsersAuth <--> D0 : Store / read / clear\npending MFA challenge
P2 <--> D1 : MFA secret,\nchallenge records,\nrecovery-code hashes

UsersAcademic <--> P7 : Assignment create / list
UsersAcademic <--> P3 : Submission / review /\nmetadata or content retrieval
UsersAcademic <--> P4 : Grade create / update / view
UsersAcademic <--> P6 : Space create / update /\nlist + membership views

P7 <--> D1 : Assignment records +\nspace visibility checks
P7 --> P5 : Assignment audit events

P3 <--> P7 : Assignment visibility /\nowner checks
P3 <--> D1 : Submission metadata
P3 <--> D2 : Ciphertext storage / read
P3 --> P5 : Submission audit events

P4 <--> P7 : Assignment ownership /\nstudent visibility checks
P4 <--> D1 : Verified state +\ngrade records
P4 --> P5 : Grade audit events

P6 <--> D1 : Space + membership data
P6 --> P5 : Space audit events

P5 --> D1 : Append audit row with\nHMAC-SHA-256 integrity chain

note right of P3
Submission protection:
- plaintext enters the backend once for handling
- SHA-256 digest and signature metadata are calculated
- content is encrypted at rest with AES-GCM
- standard metadata responses do not expose storedFileReference,
  nonce values, or wrapped content-encryption keys
end note

legend bottom
|= Diagram key |= Meaning |
| Browser Users | Duplicated for layout only: auth/MFA and academic actions |
| Role scope | Lecturer = owned assignments / created spaces only; Admin = global oversight; Student = enrolled spaces and own visible submissions/grades only |
| D0 sessionStorage | Temporary SPA-managed browser state for a pending MFA challenge only |
end legend

@enduml


